metadata.name: スーパースター
metadata.description:
‘スーパースター’ means super star in Japanese. It represents one of my super stars combing AI and Generative Art. I created an image with Midjourney and custom ASCII with TouchDesigner (node based software for visual coding). In the ASCII, there are letters of super star.

The image is re-creation of ‘Girl with a Pearl Earring (1665)’ by Johannes Vermeer with arrangements in Midjourney. The master painters are always my super stars.
